<doc id="254958" wikidata="Q40675" url="?curid=254958" title="Operation Storax">
<text>Operation Storax was a series of 47 nuclear tests conducted by the United States in 1962–1963 at the Nevada Test Site. These tests followed the &quot;Operation Fishbowl&quot; series and preceded the &quot;Operation Roller Coaster&quot; series.

==British tests==

Some accounts include the second British nuclear weapons test at the Nevada Test Site, shot &quot;Tendrac&quot;, as part of Storax. See British nuclear testing in the United States for more details.

==Tests==


