*&quot;Andrea&quot; (Billboard #41, RPM #2)) / &quot;You Don&#x27;t Phase Me&quot; — Tower 191—December 1965
*&quot;Still&quot; (Billboard #93, RPM #72)) / &quot;When You&#x27;re Not Here&quot; — Tower 224—March 1966
*&quot;Don&#x27;t Take Yourself Too Seriously&quot; / &quot;I Look Baby, I Can&#x27;t See&quot; — Tower 256—July 1966
